{"tid":581800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉事務處培訓簡報　教票站職員毋須干預「掌心雷」","createTime":"2018-03-05T15:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T01:40:57.000Z","uid":53379,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d18f4e177703ad718051f3e714377c2ecd1f8f","tid":581800,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:43:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>選舉事務處培訓簡報　教票站職員毋須干預「掌心雷」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180305/s00001/a290601ec743635484c4cf01fecbc5bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180305%2Fs00001%2Fa290601ec743635484c4cf01fecbc5bd.jpg&h=1bd3205e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月11日是立法會四個議席補選投票日，選舉事務處上月底至本月初舉行幾場培訓，向票站職員講解投票當日面對不同情況應如何處理。公民黨立法會議員譚文豪最新收到投訴，一名工作人員不滿選舉事務處培訓簡報上，教職員發現選民手掌或手持小卡寫上候選人資料，即俗稱「掌心雷」的時候，毋須干預。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪在facebook專頁發布帖文，指出每次選舉時都有政黨用「掌心雷」誘導長者投票。最近他收到一名票站職員投訴，並展示選舉事務處培訓簡報中，其中一頁有指引寫明發現「掌心雷」時毋須干預，因為有關行為並不構成罪行；但若有人公開向其他人員展示手上資料時，則須立即上前阻止，因為「可構成拉票活動」，或屬犯法。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪形容「掌心雷」乃「唔公平嘅做法」，批評選舉事務處多年來不思進取，不但沒設法取締，「而家竟然帶頭縱容」，呼籲市民3月11日一定要去投票。<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處回覆表示，選民如備有所選擇候選人資料，方便填劃選票時參考，基本上沒有問題，惟不得在投票站內向其他人展示，否則選民有可能觸犯法例。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180305/s00001/1520261803015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180305%2Fs00001%2F1520261803015&d=9WSmceSPMME4aK%2F%2FDjvC4EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=44c8fe25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180305%2Fs00001%2F1520261803015&h=8ad5bca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180305/s00001/1520261803015</a>"},{"pid":"eb0cc1f19dae887fef0fdf87189eb8c2d61fdda9","tid":581800,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係入面自己睇就冇事 咁係入面同老友記分享彪彪呢？"},{"pid":"c14d8ff02877e63d2f3c30284c864b14211479cd","tid":581800,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb0cc1f19dae887fef0fdf87189eb8c2d61fdda9","tid":581800,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係入面自己睇就冇事 咁係入面同老友記分享彪彪呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"你犯法，標錶冇事"},{"pid":"64ef7c7db29a72c7e02e6b4bfd1d78754621655f","tid":581800,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f871a4592fe56c884ab76fd4bd05a89e9e400dc","tid":581800,"uid":36478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"投票日記得陪自己屋企嘅長者去投票"},{"pid":"31613a3341672ecf11e43f5a7408bbce0da99f7f","tid":581800,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T18:45:06.000Z","msg":"種票又有<br />\n掌心雷又有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4add0a9b4a8d817d9e1c70909d7238da7b3b3a65","tid":581800,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}